r, telephone, fax, or other means.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>\r\n<p>We recognize it as our social responsibility to protect the rights and interests of individuals by using personal information only for the purposes consented to at the time of collection and by appropriately managing it during its retention period. Based on this recognition, all of our directors and employees are committed to protecting personal information.</p>\r\n<div class=\"formSubmitarea\"><input type=\"submit\" name=\"dnn$ctr860$ViewMailForm$grdMain$PageID5$repCategory$ctl02$btnInputConfirm\" value=\"Agree to the privacy policy and confirm your entry\" onclick=\"javascript:WebForm_DoPostBackWithOptions(new WebForm_PostBackOptions(&quot;dnn$ctr860$ViewMailForm$grdMain$PageID5$repCategory$ctl02$btnInputConfirm&quot;, &quot;&quot;, true, &quot;&quot;, &quot;&quot;, false, false))\" id=\"dnn_ctr860_ViewMailForm_grdMain_repCategory_0_btnInputConfirm\" /></div>\r\n\t<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"dnn$ctr860$ViewMailForm$hdnCurrentPageID\" id=\"dnn_ctr860_ViewMailForm_hdnCurrentPageID\" value=\"5\" />\r\n\t<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"dnn$ctr860$ViewMailForm$hdnCurrentFormID\" id=\"dnn_ctr860_ViewMailForm_hdnCurrentFormID\" value=\"5\" />\r\n\t<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"dnn$ctr860$ViewMailForm$hdnIsConfirm\" id=\"dnn_ctr860_ViewMailForm_hdnIsConfirm\" value=\"0\" />\r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\t</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- End_Module_860 -->\r\n</div></div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"dnn_ContentBottomPane\" class=\"ContentBottomPane DNNEmptyPane\"></div>\n  </main>\n  <footer id=\"footer\">\n    <div class=\"pagetop\"><a href=\"#Body\">Page Top</a>\r\n</div>\n    <div class=\"inner_wide\">\n      <div class=\"foot_top\">\n        <div id=\"dnn_FootENPane\" class=\"FootENPane\">\r\n<div class=\"ic-moduleheader\"></div>\r\n<section class=\"ic-modulecontent icmd-zero\">\r\n    <div class=\"icmd-actionbutton\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"dnn_ctr813_ContentPane\"><!-